                "title": "Sick Leave",
                "data": [
                    {
                        "type": "paragraph",
                        "data": "By Law, there is no sick leave in Georgia. If an employee needs to take sick leave, they can use 15 calendar days of unpaid leave."
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "paragraph",
                        "data": "Employees contracts can be paused for 40 days, after this period, the employer has the right to terminate the contract."
                    }
